    <item>
      <title>中国2024年政策目标对中美关系意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/what-china-s-2024-policy-goals-mean-for-ties-with-the-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的大型年度政策报告显示，今年中国可能必须与美国友好相处，以应对经济逆风，但加大科技投资和军费开支的雄心表明紧张局势不会消失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/what-china-s-2024-policy-goals-mean-for-ties-with-the-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将敲定信用卡滞纳金上限为 8 美元的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/biden-to-finalize-rule-to-cap-credit-card-late-fees-at-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的政府宣布了一项削减信用卡滞纳金的最终规则，这是一系列措施之一，旨在降低家庭的日常成本，这些成本在他寻求连任时影响了他的支持率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/biden-to-finalize-rule-to-cap-credit-card-late-fees-at-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>转向大选：超级星期二看什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/pivot-to-the-general-election-what-to-watch-on-super-tuesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年的超级星期二初选将把唐纳德·特朗普推向共和党提名的风口浪尖，并展开美国近代历史上最长的大选之战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/pivot-to-the-general-election-what-to-watch-on-super-tuesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的一致裁决掩盖了最高法院的意识形态分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/unanimous-trump-ruling-belies-supreme-court-s-ideological-divide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从表面上看，美国最高法院一致裁定唐纳德·特朗普可以参加今年的总统选举。但下方不远处，法庭上却充满了不和谐的声音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/unanimous-trump-ruling-belies-supreme-court-s-ideological-divide</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平的名字和口号在政府重要报告中占据主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/xi-s-name-favored-slogan-dominate-key-government-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平的名字今年在政府年度工作报告中出现16次，是他十多年前上任以来最多的一次，凸显了中国领导人的至高无上的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/xi-s-name-favored-slogan-dominate-key-government-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 09:40:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
